10
00:00:39,880 --> 00:00:42,300
That turns out not to be the case.

11
00:00:42,300 --> 00:00:43,300
Children are great imitators.

12
00:00:43,300 --> 00:00:48,649
What ends up being the case is that children will model adults, not necessarily parents,

13
00:00:48,649 --> 00:00:52,900
they&#39;ll model adults, and are able to pick up moral or immoral behaviours that way.

14
00:00:52,900 --> 00:00:56,059
Now, this experiment was highly influential at the time (Bandura et al., 1963).

15
00:00:56,059 --> 00:00:58,480
It was a really big deal.

16
00:00:58,480 --> 00:01:01,370
People were worried about children because of something that was happening in the &#39;60s,

17
00:01:01,370 --> 00:01:04,110
